reviewText:
I wanted this hole puncher for my watches. I have a very small wrist and unless I get a kids watch an adult watch band is usually too big for me and I have to end up punching another hole in the band to fit. I kept trying this on paper and it didn't punch through it, my hubby said it is mainly for punching holes into soft leather. So I tested it on a broken watch band and it did punch through a thick piece of leather pretty easily using the smallest hole. I haven't tried it on leather belts but I imagine it work work the same way.

This is a lot larger than I thought it would be. There are 6 different hole punch sizes and they snap in place so they stay. There's also a clip to hold the punch closed. The instructions are in Chinese so they didn't help at all but fortunately it is pretty easy to figure out.

